The protocol followed by the Client and Server.

1. The server will send the list of files and the information related to that file, like size, folder or file.
2. Client will selects the files which he wants to save and also specify the location of the files.
3. The client will then reply to the server with the list of files required for download. One by one:
3.1 The server will reply with the appropriate FileInputStream of the file.
3.2 The client will download the files into the preferred location.
4. Client will disconnect itself.
5. Server will continue itself.